{
  "text": "Membranes from C6 rat glioma cells were prepared as described by Piccinonna et al. [CITATION_1] with minor modifications. In brief, cells scraped in PBS and harvested, were then homogenized with a Brinkman Polytron (Kinematica AG, M\u00fcnstert\u00e4ler, Germany). After centrifugation at 37,000\u02c6g for 30 min at 4\u02ddC the resulting pellet was resuspended in ice-cold 10 mM PBS and stored at\u00b480\u02ddC until use.",
